docs.lead_paragraph: A delightful repetition of Don Pasquale, was given at NIBLO'S on Wednesday. We have certainly never heard Madame SONTAG to such pleasing advantage in Opera.

docs.lead_paragraph: The Daniel Webster has arrived at New-Orleans, bringing 300 passengers from San Juan, Nicaragua' and $90,000 in gold dust on freight, besides a considerable amount in the hands or passengers. No later California dates than we had in yesterday's paper.

docs.lead_paragraph: From the Republic, of the 8th. A meeting of the officers and members of the Coast Survey in Washington, was held at the Coast Survey Office on the 2d inst.; and, on motion of Lieut. Commanding J. J. ALMY, U. S. Navy, Prof. A. D. BACHE, Superintent of the Survey, was called to the Chair.

docs.lead_paragraph: SUPPOSED MURDER.--THE COR??NER's INQUISITION.--On Tuesday night, between 10 and 11 o'clock while Officers WALKER, WHITE, KINNEY and SHERWOOD were patroling through the Seventeenth Ward, they found a man lying on the side walk in Avenue A, quite insensible and utterly unable to speak.

docs.lead_paragraph: The Philadelphia, from Aspinwall, reached the Southwest Pass yesterday, bringing San Francisco dates to Jan. 15, and 180 passengers. The Ohio she left at Aspinwall, with one and a half millions of gold dust on freight for New-York.
